txt.en: Reduced Vitality - Known to the Orcs of Mordor as shakglob, or Stone-filth, the Stout-axes have long served as thralls of the Dark Lord of Mordor. After enduring years of tireless labour and ill-nourishment, the Stout-axes have lost some of the sturdiness they once possessed.
